4273
01:46:16,740 --> 01:46:18,620
 dakle ne treba na to pristajati

4274
01:46:18,620 --> 01:46:20,360
 niti biti žrtva

4275
01:46:20,360 --> 01:46:21,720
 niti biti ugnjetavač

4276
01:46:21,720 --> 01:46:25,000
 opće ne pristajati na tu binarnu podjelu

4277
01:46:25,000 --> 01:46:26,700
